examples.explanation:
1. Initialize cache with capacity 2, empty list and maps
2. put(1,10): Add node with key=1, value=10, freq=1 to head. Map: {1: (10, node1, 1)}
3. put(2,20): Add node with key=2, value=20, freq=1 to head. List: 2<->1. Map: {1: (10, node1, 1), 2: (20, node2, 1)}
4. get(1): Key 1 exists, move node1 to head, increment freq to 2. List: 1<->2. Map: {1: (10, node1, 2), 2: (20, node2, 1)}
5. put(3,30): Capacity full, evict tail node2 (key=2). Add node3 to head. List: 3<->1. Map: {1: (10, node1, 2), 3: (30, node3, 1)}
6. getMostFrequent(): Scan frequencies: key1 freq=2, key3 freq=1. Max freq=2 at key=1, return value=10

